    <summary>OpenKlant customer interaction management integration for Nextcloud</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[OpenKlant Integration for Nextcloud

Integrate OpenKlant customer interaction registry with your Nextcloud instance.

- Customer contact management from Nextcloud
- Klantinteracties API integration
- Link customer interactions with cases and documents
- Common Ground / ZGW API compliant
- Free and open source under EUPL

**Requirements:**
- OpenKlant server instance
- Nextcloud 28 or higher
    ]]></description>
